-1.title: No Spank You
-1.plot: In need for a new job, Frankie sets out on the hunt. Things seem to be going well when she gets asked to come in for an interview. Thinking she's back on track and in control, Frankie enjoys the prospect of a real professional job in the CBD. Although things aren't what they seem.

imdb.plot outline: The Unfortunate Files is a new comedy web series following the day to day life of Frankie Files, a naive, passive aggressive and uncomfortably awkward girl on the verge of adulthood. Frankie is constantly being thrown curve balls and is forced to face the realities of growing up all the while trying to keep her head above water.
